ype|Grass}}.\n* Comfey is the smallest fully evolved Pokémon.\n\n===Origin===\nComfey appears to be a living {{wp|lei (garland)|lei}}.\n\n====Name origin====\nComfey may be a combination of \'\'comfy\'\', \'\'comfort\'\', \'\'{{wp|comfrey}}\'\', \'\'fey\'\', and \'\'lei\'\'.\n\nCuwawa may be a combination of \'\'cure\'\', 輪 \'\'wa\'\' (ring), and フラワー \'\'furawā\'\' (flower).\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=Fairy|type2=Fairy\n|ja=キュワワー \'\'Cuwawa\'\'|jameaning=From \'\'cure\'\', {{tt|輪 \'\'wa\'\'|ring}}, and \'\'flower\'\'\n|fr=Guérilande|frmeaning=From {{tt|\'\'guérir\'\'|cure}} and {{tt|\'\'guirlande\'\'|garland}}\n|es=Comfey|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|de=Curelei|demeaning=From \'\'cure\'\' and \'\'{{wp|Lei (garland)|lei}}\'\'\n|it=Comfey|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=큐아링 \'\'Kyuaring\'\'|komeaning=From \'\'cure\'\' and \'\'ring\'\'\n|zh_cmn=花療環環 / 花疗环环 \'\'Huāliáohuánhuán\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=From {{tt|花環 / 花环 \'\'huāhuán\'\'|garland}} and {{tt|療法 \'\'liáofǎ\'\'|therapy}}\n|zh_yue=花療環環 \'\'Fālìuhwàahnwàahn\'\'|zh_yuemeaning=From {{tt|花環 \'\'fāwàahn\'\'|garland}} and {{tt|療法 \'\'lìuhfaat\'\'|therapy}}\n|ru=Комфей \'\'Komfey\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name}}\n{{-}}\n\n==Related articles==\n* [[Nurse Joy\'s Comfey]]\n* [[Brock\'s Comfey]]\n\n==Notes==\n<references/>\n\n==External links==\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Fairy}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Fairy|prevnum=763|prev=Tsareena|nextnum=765|next=Oranguru}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Curelei]]\n[[es:Comfey]]\n[[fr:Guérilande]]\n[[it:Comfey]]\n[[ja:キュワワー]]\n[[zh:花疗环环]]'}